00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:09,750
♪If we meet again, don't hug me♪

234
00:10:09,810 --> 00:10:12,850
♪I don't want it this way♪

235
00:10:12,850 --> 00:10:16,470
♪I can't see or force a smile♪

236
00:10:16,470 --> 00:10:19,950
♪I'll just forget it♪

237
00:10:20,210 --> 00:10:24,150
♪If I can't cover
the corners of my eyes♪

238
00:10:24,620 --> 00:10:27,740
♪How will my tears roll down?♪

239
00:10:28,250 --> 00:10:35,700
♪You actually know it's so hard for me♪
